HOMEPAGE='https://wiki.gnome.org/Apps/Atomix'
SUMMARY='Puzzle game where you move atoms to build a molecule.'
DESCRIPTION="You start the game with the map filled with walls and a few atoms, which you can move in any direction. However, the atoms won't stop until they hit a wall or another atom. You can see a preview of what molecule you have to build, and you have to do your best to find where to buil the molecule, and move the atoms there."
DOWNLOADS="https://download.gnome.org/sources/${PN}/$(ever range 1-2)/${PNV}.tar.xz"
SLOT='0'
#LICENCES=''
PLATFORMS="~x86 ~amd64"

